{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6537aa9c25","title":"关于优待日军停房的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03722279b4","index":0,"year":1939,"month":2,"day":18,"articleId":"6537aa9c25"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"411376fc38","type":"paragraph","text":"关于优待日军停房的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"6537aa9c25"},{"id":"2883275ab5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年2月18日）一、敌军战斗力较前大为减弱，政治情绪更坏，以后在战斗中停获之日军停房应尽量释放，多则不超过两星期，情况许可时当场释放，多加宣传优待，严禁枪系及其他悔导行为，在各后方训练之仔房可的情处理，如不妨碍军事秘密亦可释放，借此降低日军之作战决心而动摇其军心，以利于粉碎敌之进攻二、据说日军多数部队中国人占三分之二，日本人仅占三分之一，运输队则全属韩人，是否属实请就地调查电告。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"6537aa9c25"},{"id":"1a22bf617a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛王评","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"6537aa9c25"},{"id":"e8d9bbad17","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日[I]这是毛泽东和王醇样、谭致联名给八路军、新四军各部的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"6537aa9c25"}],"page":{"id":"47778ac26e","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"6537aa9c25","start":231,"end":231}}}},"__N_SSG":true}